high_descs: Turn to your left then straight and back around to face the alarm clocks on the table.
Pick up the alarm clock towards the back.
Turn left with the alarm clock and walk straight and turn right facing the desk.
Place the alarm clock on the desk in the front.
anns.task_desc: Take an alarm clock to move it to the desk.

high_descs: Turn around, turn right, and face the brown table.
Pick up the clock on the left from the brown table.
Turn left and go to the brown desk next to the brown table.
Put the clock on the brown desk.
anns.task_desc: Put one clock on the desk.

high_descs: Turn around towards the alarm clocks on the desk.
Pick up the alarm clock which is closest to the wall.
Walk to the left side of the desk, by the chair.
Put the alarm clock on the front of the desk, to the right of the chair.
anns.task_desc: Move an alarm clock from one end of a desk to the other.
